snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk: Spotted Together in Chile after being seen sharing a kiss.
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Elon Musk: Spotted Together in Chile after being seen sharing a kiss.

The former couple was seen on vacation in Chile and enjoying a dinner with friends that included the brother of Tesla CEO Kimbal Musk. The restaurant where they were having dinner, El Taringa, published a photo of the crew with the actress and the engineer sitting next to each other in the left corner of the photo on Friday night. Heard, 31, was staring at the table while Musk, 46, was enjoying a conversation with his fellow diners. What an inspiration to have had Kimbal Musk and his family in Taringa. Thank you for sharing your ideas about sustainable supply chains The Kitchen and its whole concept is a model to follow. While the actress of the Justice League has not published photos of her with Musk, she did share photos of her vacation on Saturday while having fun on the beach with a dress, a hat and a necklace of roses.

Heard and Musk made headlines a few days before Christmas when they were photographed sharing a kiss outside a Los Angeles restaurant. The photos left the fans speculating whether the two had rekindled their romance four months after the separation. A source close to Musk said the duo was just having a friendly visit. Amber invited Elon to his favorite breakfast place in Texas, said Musk's friend from HomeState Restaurant, Los Feliz, California. where the photos were taken. They shared a quick goodbye kiss. They are still just friends, without trying to be together again.
